summary: Travel back the to ancient ruin of Skuldafn
descriptionHtml: Skuldafn was once a great Nordic city, So large that it even housed the only known portal to the realm of Sovngarde, In the vanilla game this location could be accessed only once, When you cleared Skuldafn you were unable to ever return, This mod changes that by marking Skuldafn as a location on your map that can be fast traveled to, This mod also allows you to fast travel away from Skuldafn as well as Sovngarde if you reenter the Sovngarde portal
author: JACKZTHERIPPER
